{"type":"message","id":"f4501e8c","parentId":"55b19343","timestamp":"2026-04-01T19:19:08.558Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's only one session - the cron session itself. The cron job was triggered and is running now. The session only has the cron system's messages, no user messages. So this is a \"空闲\" (idle/no user conversation) state.\n\nNow I need to execute the autonomous learning:\n1. Search for latest news on enterprise digital transformation, intelligent security, network system integration, IT operations services\n2. Organize 3-5 key pieces of information\n3. Save to /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\nLet me first check if there's any existing content in the learning notes file, and also check the skills directory for a web search skill.\n\n\nI'll need to search the web for current information and check what learning resources already exist in the workspace.","thinkingSignature":"0fe39a0102fa25d583e8c33275f28c97c50161ee016b0d15d8e076c5b22427e6"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到无活跃用户对话，执行自主学习。先查一下是否有相关技能和现有学习笔记。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ecp7tnqcxmy4_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ecp7tnqcxmy4_2","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1674,"output":261,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45916,"cost":{"input":0.0005022,"output":0.00031319999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00213483}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775071142491}}
{"type":"message","id":"2df49eb1","parentId":"f4501e8c","timestamp":"2026-04-01T19:19:08.569Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ecp7tnqcxmy4_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"read\",\n  \"error\": \"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md'\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"read","error":"ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md'"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775071148564}}
{"type":"message","id":"5d2b46c2","parentId":"2df49eb1","timestamp":"2026-04-01T19:19:08.574Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ecp7tnqcxmy4_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 学习笔记 - 行业动态\n\n**更新时间**：2026-04-02 03:08（深夜自主学习第二轮）\n\n---\n\n## 一、企业数字化转型（政策面）\n\n**核心数据**：\n- 2026-2028年设立**200亿元专项资金**支持中小企业数字化转型，云服务/智能设备购置补贴30%\n- 制造业中小企业研发费用加计扣除比例提升至**120%**\n- 工信部启动\"工业数据筑基行动\"，推动AI赋能高质量行业数据集\n\n**关键信号**：\n- 北京：最高支持**500万元**支持企业数字化转型\n- 广东：目标推动**超4000家规上工业企业**数字化转型\n- 汽车行业：2027年目标数智技术深度集成研产销服全环节\n\n**对道简的意义**：政策红利窗口期，B端数字化服务需求持续释放\n\n---\n\n## 二、智能安防与弱电工程（市场面）\n\n**核心数据**：\n- 弱电工程市场2026年预计达**8000亿元**，年复合增长率12.3%\n- 安防系统2023年市场规模**2150亿元**，占弱电市场31.5%\n\n**技术趋势**：\n- **国产化加速**：核心设备性能比肩进口，价格低15%-30%，政策倾斜下招投标优先\n- **传输升级**：PoE++与5G/6G专网取代铜缆成为主流\n- **AI深度融合**：从\"被动监控\"向\"实时预警、智能决策\"进化\n- **金融行业**：智慧网点AI监控覆盖率100%，事件处置效率提升60%\n\n**行业挑战**：总包压价、利润压缩，需从\"设备搬运\"向\"技术服务\"转型\n\n**对道简的意义**：AI赋能安防系统、弱电智能化工程是核心增长赛道\n\n---\n\n## 三、IT运维与网络系统集成（技术面）\n\n**技术架构变革**：\n- 63%中国企业生产环境部署**Kubernetes集群**，70%采用多云架构\n- 50%以上中大型企业使用**3个以上云平台**，催生\"全栈监控\"需求\n\n**智能化渗透**：\n- **65%**中大型企业部署AIOps工具\n- 网络管理自动化比例从35%升至**60%**\n- 生成式AI用于20%的初始网络配置\n\n**模式创新**：\n- **NaaS（网络即服务）崛起**：30%中大型企业采用\n- 60%新SD-WAN购买纳入**SASE方案**\n- 运维外包从\"成本控制工具\"升级为\"数字化战略支点\"\n\n**对道简的意义**：IT全周期运维服务需向AIOps智能运维、云原生架构服务能力升级\n\n---\n\n## 四、2026年最新政策与行业动态（2026-04-02补充）\n\n### 4.1 企业数字化转型新动向\n- **工信部\"工业数据筑基行动\"（2026年3月启动）**：目标到2026年底实现\"六个一批\"——培育行业数据合作联合体、建设重点行业数据可信互联平台、汇聚行业数据资源、攻关数据关键技术、研制工业数据标准、打造高质量标准化可流通行业数据集，赋能行业大模型和工业智能体应用落地\n- **工业互联网平台高质量发展行动方案（2026-2028年）**：持续提升工业互联网平台发展质量\n- **国家数据局2026年重点工作**：加快建立全国统一数据产权登记制度；建设全国一体化算力网；推动数据产业发展，培育数字产业集群；面向医疗、科学、交通等16个重点领域打造高质量数据集\n- **\"人工智能+制造\"行动方案**：2026年打造千个工业智能体、五百个典型应用场景，覆盖钢铁、机械、轻工、纺织、电子等主流行业，AI从头部企业向中小制造企业普及\n- **汽车行业数字化转型实施方案（2026年1月）**：到2027年数智技术在研产销服环节深度集成，行业供给和公共服务体系逐步完善\n\n### 4.2 智能安防行业新动向\n- **AI大模型+具身智能成为核心技术**：海康威视、华为等头部企业推动安防向\"感知-判断-处置\"全链路闭环发展\n- **四足机器人安防商业化加速**：如康迪科技与前海康威视团队合作推出自主巡逻、多模态感知系统，计划2026年进入美国市场\n- **中国安防市场增速领先全球**：年复合增长率15.1%，占全球份额35%，预计2026年规模1500-2000亿美元\n- **隐私合规压力加剧**：《数据安全法》《个人信息保护法》深入实施，推动\"云存储加密\"\"本地化处理\"技术方案成为标配\n- **行业展会动态**：2026年济南安博会、北京安博会汇聚400余家企业，集中展示AI+安防成果\n\n### 4.3 IT运维服务行业新动向\n- **AI Agent推动\"自主运维\"落地**：从\"规则驱动\"向\"认知驱动\"跃迁，具备故障推理、业务影响分析、处置后果模拟及最优策略推荐能力\n- **NLOps（自然语言运维）兴起**：通过对话指令执行诊断与修复\n- **可观测性成为标准配置**：日志、指标、追踪三位一体融合，整合用户体验数据，实现端到端根因分析\n- **绿色IT运维成为新竞争力**：通过云电脑替代传统终端、AI节能系统动态调节数据中心能耗等技术降低碳排放，ESG报告中体现运维绿色价值\n- **国产化替代规模化**：国产化监控平台在政府、能源、交通等关键领域加速替代\n- **运维外包行业洗牌加剧**：AI成为分水岭，具备AI能力的服务商通过预测性维护显著降低故障率，行业向\"效果付费\"转型\n\n### 4.4 网络系统集成行业新动向\n- **高带宽+自治网络成为方向**：市场向400G高带宽演进，为L4级自治网络（自我修复、自我优化、自我演进）奠定基础\n- **融合架构成为主流**：AIoT+边缘计算+零信任安全+SDN/NFV组合方案广泛应用，43%的千万级项目已采用此类技术组合\n- **iPaaS平台低代码化**：预计2026年超70%的企业轻量级集成场景将由业务端自主实现\n- **多云系统集成深度融合**：打破云间壁垒，提升跨平台协同效率\n- **零信任安全成为标配**：零信任架构、先进加密技术应对复杂网络威胁\n\n---\n\n## 五、关键洞察（供姚总参考）\n\n| 维度 | 核心趋势 | 对道简的启示 |\n|------|----------|-------------|\n| 政策面 | 200亿专项+研发加计扣除120%+工业数据筑基行动 | B端数字化需求持续释放，招投标机会增多，工业数据+AI融合是重点方向 |\n| 市场面 | 安防CAGR 15.1%领跑全球/弱电市场8000亿 | 智能化安防工程+国产替代是增长双引擎；四足机器人等新形态安防商业化加速 |\n| 技术面 | AIOps/云原生/NaaS/绿色IT/国产替代 | 运维服务需升级至智能化、云原生、绿色化；网络系统集成需掌握AIoT+边缘+零信任融合方案 |\n| 网络集成 | 400G带宽/L4自治网络/iPaaS低代码化 | 高带宽网络建设+智能运维平台是系统性集成业务升级方向 |\n\n---\n\n**备注**：以上信息综合自国家工信部政策文件及行业研究数据，具体以官方发布为准。"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775071148571}}
{"type":"message","id":"14c6fb39","parentId":"5d2b46c2","timestamp":"2026-04-01T19:19:15.860Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's already existing content in the learning notes file. It's quite comprehensive. Now I need to search for the latest information on enterprise digital transformation, intelligent security, network system integration, and IT operations services to update the learning notes.\n\nLet me search for the latest news on these topics. I'll use the web-search skill if available, or directly use exec to use curl/wget commands.\n\nActually, let me check if the web-search skill exists.","thinkingSignature":"2322158795423da3550c8e69957d638246d6d895508eff0804ecceedfc55738b"},{"type":"text","text":"现有学习笔记内容较新（4月2日凌晨3:08更新）。让我搜索最新动态看是否有更新的信息。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bkenbyzu1l35_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"~/.agents/skills/web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3568,"output":149,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47698,"cost":{"input":0.0010704,"output":0.00017879999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0025686299999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775071148574}}
{"type":"message","id":"e2805ed4","parentId":"14c6fb39","timestamp":"2026-04-01T19:19:15.867Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_bkenbyzu1l35_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: web-search\ndescription: \"Web search and content extraction with Tavily and Exa via inference.sh CLI. Apps: Tavily Search, Tavily Extract, Exa Search, Exa Answer, Exa Extract. Capabilities: AI-powered search, content extraction, direct answers, research. Use for: research, RAG pipelines, fact-checking, content aggregation, agents. Triggers: web search, tavily, exa, search api, content extraction, research, internet search, ai search, search assistant, web scraping, rag, perplexity alternative\"\nallowed-tools: Bash(infsh *)\n---\n\n# Web Search & Extraction\n\nSearch the web and extract content via [inference.sh](https://inference.sh) CLI.\n\n![Web Search & Extraction](https://cloud.inference.sh/app/files/u/4mg21r6ta37mpaz6ktzwtt8krr/01kgndqjxd780zm2j3rmada6y8.jpeg)\n\n## Quick Start\n\n> Requires inference.sh CLI (`infsh`). Get installation instructions: `npx skills add inference-sh/skills@agent-tools`\n\n```bash\ninfsh login\n\n# Search the web\ninfsh app run tavily/search-assistant --input '{\"query\": \"latest AI developments 2024\"}'\n```\n\n\n## Available Apps\n\n### Tavily\n\n| App | App ID | Description |\n|-----|--------|-------------|\n| Search Assistant | `tavily/search-assistant` | AI-powered search with answers |\n| Extract | `tavily/extract` | Extract content from URLs |\n\n### Exa\n\n| App | App ID | Description |\n|-----|--------|-------------|\n| Search | `exa/search` | Smart web search with AI |\n| Answer | `exa/answer` | Direct factual answers |\n| Extract | `exa/extract` | Extract and analyze web content |\n\n## Examples\n\n### Tavily Search\n\n```bash\ninfsh app run tavily/search-assistant --input '{\n  \"query\": \"What are the best practices for building AI agents?\"\n}'\n```\n\nReturns AI-generated answers with sources and images.\n\n### Tavily Extract\n\n```bash\ninfsh app run tavily/extract --input '{\n  \"urls\": [\"https://example.com/article1\", \"https://example.com/article2\"]\n}'\n```\n\nExtracts clean text and images from multiple URLs.\n\n### Exa Search\n\n```bash\ninfsh app run exa/search --input '{\n  \"query\": \"machine learning frameworks comparison\"\n}'\n```\n\nReturns highly relevant links with context.\n\n### Exa Answer\n\n```bash\ninfsh app run exa/answer --input '{\n  \"question\": \"What is the population of Tokyo?\"\n}'\n```\n\nReturns direct factual answers.\n\n### Exa Extract\n\n```bash\ninfsh app run exa/extract --input '{\n  \"url\": \"https://example.com/research-paper\"\n}'\n```\n\nExtracts and analyzes web page content.\n\n## Workflow: Research + LLM\n\n```bash\n# 1. Search for information\ninfsh app run tavily/search-assistant --input '{\n  \"query\": \"latest developments in quantum computing\"\n}' > search_results.json\n\n# 2. Analyze with Claude\ninfsh app run openrouter/claude-sonnet-45 --input '{\n  \"prompt\": \"Based on this research, summarize the key trends: <search-results>\"\n}'\n```\n\n## Workflow: Extract + Summarize\n\n```bash\n# 1. Extract content from URL\ninfsh app run tavily/extract --input '{\n  \"urls\": [\"https://example.com/long-article\"]\n}' > content.json\n\n# 2. Summarize with LLM\ninfsh app run openrouter/claude-haiku-45 --input '{\n  \"prompt\": \"Summarize this article in 3 bullet points: <content>\"\n}'\n```\n\n## Use Cases\n\n- **Research**: Gather information on any topic\n- **RAG**: Retrieval-augmented generation\n- **Fact-checking**: Verify claims with sources\n- **Content aggregation**: Collect data from multiple sources\n- **Agents**: Build research-capable AI agents\n\n## Related Skills\n\n```bash\n# Full platform skill (all 150+ apps)\nnpx skills add inference-sh/skills@agent-tools\n\n# LLM models (combine with search for RAG)\nnpx skills add inference-sh/skills@llm-models\n\n# Image generation\nnpx skills add inference-sh/skills@ai-image-generation\n```\n\nBrowse all apps: `infsh app list`\n\n## Documentation\n\n- [Adding Tools to Agents](https://inference.sh/docs/agents/adding-tools) - Equip agents with search\n- [Building a Research Agent](https://inference.sh/blog/guides/research-agent) - LLM + search integration guide\n- [Tool Integration Tax](https://inference.sh/blog/tools/integration-tax) - Why pre-built tools matter\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775071155862}}
